---
description: "Rules for modifying CRD types and schema"
globs: ["api/v1beta1/**/*.go"]
---

- The canonical type is `CostManagementMetricsConfig`; `MetricsConfig` is a type alias
- Add kubebuilder validation markers for new fields
- Default values use `+kubebuilder:default=` markers
- Run `make manifests` after any changes to regenerate CRD YAML
- Run `make verify-manifests` to confirm generated files are up to date
